high_descs: turn right, face toilet
pick up center candle from toilet
go to lower end cabinet to the right of toilet
open cabinet, place candle in cabinet, close cabinet
go to toilet to the left
pick up candle on the left
go to lower end cabinet to the right of toilet
open cabinet, place candle behind candle in cabinet, close cabinet
anns.task_desc: place two candles in lower left cabinet

high_descs: Go forward a step, turn right to face the toilet and sink.
Take the middle candle from the toilet tank.
Turn around, go forward a step, turn right, go forward a step, turn right.
Put the candle in the bottom left cabinet beneath the sink.
Move forward to the toilet.
Take the left candle from the toilet tank.
Turn around, go forward a step, turn around.
Put the candle in the bottom left cabinet beneath the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles in a cabinet.

high_descs: Step forward, then turn right and look in the space between the sink and toilet.
Pick up the center candle on the top of the toilet.
Turn around, walk forward, turn right, step forward and then turn right to face the toilet.
Open the cabinet door on bottom right, place the candle inside, close the door.
Step forward to the toilet.
Pick up the left candle on the toilet.
Turn around, step forward, then turn around again to face the toilet.
Open the bottom cabinet drawer and place the candle inside.
anns.task_desc: Place two candles in the lower cabinet.
